Quick howto:


  SETUP PROCESS

    cd ~
    git clone git://github.com/mattx86/symfony-aliases.git
    mkdir tools
    ln -s symfony-aliases/* tools/
    nano tools/.symfony-projects.inc.sh  # edit config
    export PATH="$HOME/tools;$PATH"

  USAGE EXAMPLE

    cd sites/projectA/config
    scc  # equivalent of: cd .. ; ./symfony cc ; cd config
